{"tid":146582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東區醫院再爆18歲男病人遭44歲男院友非禮","createTime":"2017-03-07T08:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T09:57:44.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2fa8901532f5caeb86a3c202ee38826622c7cc4","tid":146582,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170307/large/1488873367_cf0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F1488873367_cf0b.jpg&h=eba2cb07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東區醫院又爆出男病人遭院友非禮的風化案件。今晨7時，警方接獲醫院職員報案，指院內一名18歲男病人，疑被44歲男院友非禮，警員接報到場，經初步調查後，拘捕該名44歲男院友。案件交由東區警區刑事調查隊第八隊跟進。今次已是個多月內爆出第4名公院男病人遭侵犯事件。<br />\n<br />\n上月13日，留醫東區醫院的17歲精神科男病人會見醫生時透露．遭一名年長的男院友非禮包括摸下體，醫護人員報警，警方拘捕69歲男院友。本報正向東區醫院查詢。"},{"pid":"cb067e1ebc7579c9359c9acadfd22456debb6349","tid":146582,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4955f26c59331b914299fe43c997a618b84ab56d","tid":146582,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:54:06.000Z","msg":"痴線，醫院都咁樣，監獄真係日日執番梘"},{"pid":"17f5503aac4dd150720d652d9760ac4cd2e40033","tid":146582,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:54:34.000Z","msg":"又係精神科"},{"pid":"d299c89db5756a46923b119af4371b6a5fd07782","tid":146582,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"男仲危險過女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}